data.description: Charming 3BR/2BA Corner Home in Aliana – 2,239 sq ft of Elegance    Welcome to this stunning home in the desirable Aliana subdivision, boasting an open floor plan with split bedrooms for privacy. Highlights include a spacious living area perfect for entertaining, a modern kitchen, and a serene master suite. The large backyard on a corner lot offers endless possibilities for outdoor enjoyment. Enjoy the top-rated schools and vibrant community atmosphere. A home not just for living, but for making memories.
